            <section class="" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; padding-left: 5px; padding-right: 5px; margin-bottom: 4px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(213, 95, 49);">
              <p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">货基债市也处于“多事之秋”</strong></span></p>
            </section>
            <section style="border-top-width: 2px; border-top-style: dotted; border-top-color: rgb(95, 94, 102); width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"></section>
          </section>
